#### sample input and options for diffus
#    This program calculates the diffusion in specified dimensions
#
@topo ex.top
#     topology file
@pbc r
#     periodic boundary conditions -> rectangular
#
@time 0 0.1
#     the starting time and increment between between frames in
#     trajectory
#
@dim x y z
#     a list of the dimensions to be taken into account
#
@atoms s:O?
#     AtomSpecifier for the atoms to follow
#
@ref exref.coo
#     reference coordinates for t=0. If not specified the first frame in
#     traj is taken
#
@traj ex.tr
#     trajectory files

